        <text>
            <body>
                <p>Ego <persName key="d1e27507" xml:id="d1e161819">Andreas <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324487" xml:id="d1e161821" corresp="Montbard (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Montis Barri</placeName>
                        dominus</persName> testificor scire volentibus quod <persName key="d1e27514" xml:id="d1e161825">Viardus de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325029" xml:id="d1e161827" corresp="Seneveii">Seneveio</placeName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e27520" xml:id="d1e161830">Johannes frater
                        ejus</persName> et <persName key="d1e27526" xml:id="d1e161833">
                        <app>
                            <lem>Renerius</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D #a">Reinerius</rdg>
                        </app> de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324430" xml:id="d1e161840" corresp="Champ-d'Oiseau (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Chaudoisel</foreign>
                        </placeName>
                    </persName> dederunt ecclesie <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#282689" xml:id="d1e161844" corresp="abbaye Notre-Dame de Fontenay (1119 -)">
                        <app>
                            <lem>Fonteneti</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D #a">Fontenetensi</rdg>
                        </app>
                    </orgName> totam terram arabilem quam habebant a <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324453" xml:id="d1e161852" corresp="Fontenay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Fonteneto</placeName> usque <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324475" xml:id="d1e161855" corresp="Marmagne (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                        <app>
                            <lem>Marmaniam</lem>
                            <rdg wit="#D">Marm</rdg>
                            <rdg wit="#Dpc #a">Marineium</rdg>
                        </app>
                    </placeName>
                    <app>
                        <lem>
                            <witEnd wit="#D #a" />
                        </lem>
                    </app>et quod habebant ad <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325272" xml:id="d1e161867" corresp="Altam ripam">Altam ripam</placeName> et quod habebant in <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#325253" xml:id="d1e161870" corresp="Correson">
                        <foreign>Curtresum</foreign>
                    </placeName> a chimino susum versus. Habebunt autem pro his omnibus singulis
                    annis <num>xii</num> denarios census. Hoc donum fecit <persName key="d1e27532" xml:id="d1e161878">Viardus</persName> prius de sua parte et habuit inde
                    equum <num>vi</num>librarum. Postea de sua parte fecerunt donum <persName key="d1e27538" xml:id="d1e161887">Johannes</persName> et <persName key="d1e27544" xml:id="d1e161890">Renerius</persName> apud <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324453" xml:id="d1e161894" corresp="Fontenay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Fontenetum</placeName> et <persName key="d1e27551" xml:id="d1e161897">Viardus</persName> hoc laudavit <app>
                        <lem>
                            <witStart wit="#D #a" />
                        </lem>
                    </app>coram me et <persName key="d1e27557" xml:id="d1e161904">domino meo
                        Anserico <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324959" xml:id="d1e161906" corresp="Monte Regali">Montis
                            Regii</placeName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e27563" xml:id="d1e161909">Anserico
                        juvene</persName>, <persName key="d1e27569" xml:id="d1e161912">Hugone quoque
                        de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324331" xml:id="d1e161914" corresp="Nesle-et-Massoult (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">Nigellis</placeName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e27575" xml:id="d1e161921">Bernardo
                            <addName>Nariodi</addName>
                    </persName> et <persName key="d1e27581" xml:id="d1e161926">Andrea de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324452" xml:id="d1e161928" corresp="Fontaines-en-Duesmois (Côte-d'Or, Châtillon-sur-Seine)">Fontanis</placeName>
                    </persName>
                    <app>
                        <lem>
                            <witEnd wit="#D #a" />
                            <witDetail wit="#D #a">Fin omise et remplacée par "etc."</witDetail>
                        </lem>
                    </app>. <persName key="d1e27588" xml:id="d1e161936">Johannes</persName> habuit
                    pro sua parte <num>lx</num> solidos et <persName key="d1e27594" xml:id="d1e161942">Renerio</persName> de sua parte dedit alibi scambium
                    eidem <persName key="d1e27600" xml:id="d1e161946">Renerio</persName>
                    placitum.</p>
